{"tid":1787228,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[當年今日] 警校畢業禮 林鄭月娥寄語警員注意一言一行","createTime":"2019-12-17T19:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T13:11:50.000Z","uid":30506,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"826c720157d1f3c9fd28171d2ee317a50b562ce4","tid":1787228,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"2017年11月25日<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥出席警察學院結業禮時指，市民對公務員的要求日增，寄語警務人員要有承擔、熱誠及同理心。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥致辭時，引用國家主席習近平今年七月訪港會見特區政府問責官員時的一句說話，「一榮皆榮、一損俱損」，勉勵警員要記在心中。她指出，對於一個三萬人的警隊，不可以因為一個人損害整個警隊的名聲，要齊心一致維護警隊。<br />\n<br />\n而在林鄭月娥致辭期間，一名獲頒施禮榮盾及榮譽警棍的女督察感到身體不適，需要由在場人員扶離現場。<br />\n<br />\n醬：<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=244486&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D244486%26refer%3DShare&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Bug0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=9b8abead\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D244486%26refer%3DShare&h=32fa17fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=244486&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"22485287bd5444b3147fd73f7feef329876066ae","tid":1787228,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T21:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203a28b1e42774daf766b9e767dd154554c079a4","tid":1787228,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8641d17daf35ae73f1bdcfce8fca096e90370